                response: "üìÖ **Let's Plan Your Perfect Nangal Trip!**\n\n**üïê 1-Day Quick Tour:**\n‚Ä¢ Morning: Bhakra Dam visit\n‚Ä¢ Afternoon: Govind Sagar Lake\n‚Ä¢ Evening: Sutlej Park sunset\n\n**üïê 2-Day Comprehensive:**\n‚Ä¢ Day 1: Dam, Lake, Township\n‚Ä¢ Day 2: Hills, Temple, Village\n\n**üïê 3-Day Relaxed Experience:**\n‚Ä¢ Day 1: Arrival + Dam exploration\n‚Ä¢ Day 2: Nature trails + Bird watching\n‚Ä¢ Day 3: Cultural sites + Shopping\n\n**Tell me:**\n‚Ä¢ How many days do you have?\n‚Ä¢ Your interests (nature/culture/photography/adventure)?\n‚Ä¢ Group size and budget?\n‚Ä¢ Any specific requirements?"
              },
              timing: {
