                response: "üå§Ô∏è **Best Time to Visit Nangal:**\n\n**üå∏ Spring (March-May)** - EXCELLENT\n‚Ä¢ Temperature: 15-25¬∞C\n‚Ä¢ Perfect weather for all activities\n‚Ä¢ Clear skies, ideal for photography\n‚Ä¢ Blooming flowers and pleasant breeze\n\n**üåßÔ∏è Monsoon (June-September)** - GOOD\n‚Ä¢ Temperature: 20-30¬∞C\n‚Ä¢ Lush green landscapes\n‚Ä¢ Dam at full capacity (spectacular views)\n‚Ä¢ Some outdoor activities may be limited\n\n**‚ùÑÔ∏è Winter (October-February)** - VERY GOOD\n‚Ä¢ Temperature: 5-20¬∞C\n‚Ä¢ Cool and comfortable for long walks\n‚Ä¢ Crystal clear mountain views\n‚Ä¢ Perfect for sightseeing and photography\n\n**‚òÄÔ∏è Summer (April-June)** - AVOID\n‚Ä¢ Temperature: 25-40¬∞C\n‚Ä¢ Can be uncomfortably hot\n‚Ä¢ Limited outdoor activities\n\n**Recommendation: October-March for best experience!**"
