                response: "üè® **Accommodation Options in Nangal:**\n\n**üåü Premium Hotels (‚Çπ3000-5000/night):**\n‚Ä¢ Hotel Bhakra View - Lake facing rooms, restaurant, AC\n‚Ä¢ Nangal Regency - Modern amenities, swimming pool\n‚Ä¢ Dam View Resort - Scenic location, conference facilities\n\n**üè° Mid-Range Options (‚Çπ1500-3000/night):**\n‚Ä¢ Government Guest House - Clean, reliable, central location\n‚Ä¢ Tourist Lodge - Basic amenities, budget-friendly\n‚Ä¢ Sutlej Inn - Family-friendly, restaurant attached\n\n**üè† Budget Stays (‚Çπ800-1500/night):**\n‚Ä¢ Local Homestays - Authentic cultural experience\n‚Ä¢ Dharamshala accommodations - Religious stay\n‚Ä¢ Backpacker hostels - Shared facilities\n\n**üèïÔ∏è Unique Experiences:**\n‚Ä¢ Lakeside camping (seasonal)\n‚Ä¢ Forest rest houses\n‚Ä¢ Government circuit houses\n\n**Need help choosing based on your budget and preferences?**"
              },
              food: {
                keywords: ['food', 'eat', 'restaurant', 'local cuisine', 'dining', 'hungry', 'meal', 'dish'],
                response: "üçΩÔ∏è **Culinary Delights of Nangal:**\n\n**ü•ò Must-Try Local Specialties:**\n‚Ä¢ **Punjabi Thali** - Complete traditional meal with variety\n‚Ä¢ **Makki di Roti & Sarson da Saag** - Winter specialty with butter\n‚Ä¢ **Fresh Fish Curry** - From Govind Sagar Lake\n‚Ä¢ **Chole Bhature** - Spicy chickpeas with fried bread\n‚Ä¢ **Lassi & Kulfi** - Traditional drinks and desserts\n‚Ä¢ **Rajma Chawal** - Kidney beans with rice\n\n**üç¥ Best Dining Spots:**\n‚Ä¢ **Hotel Restaurants** - Multi-cuisine, air-conditioned\n‚Ä¢ **Local Dhabas** - Authentic roadside eateries\n‚Ä¢ **Lakeside Cafes** - Scenic dining with lake views\n‚Ä¢ **Street Food Stalls** - Budget-friendly local flavors\n‚Ä¢ **Community Kitchens** - Gurudwara free meals\n\n**üå± Vegetarian Paradise** - Excellent options available!\n**üå∂Ô∏è Spice Level** - Can be customized for your taste\n\n**Want recommendations for specific meals or dietary requirements?**"
              },
              transport: {
                keywords: ['transport', 'travel', 'bus', 'train', 'car', 'reach', 'how to get', 'journey'],
                response: "üöó **How to Reach Nangal:**\n\n**‚úàÔ∏è By Air:**\n‚Ä¢ **Chandigarh Airport** (60 km, 1.5 hours)\n‚Ä¢ Regular flights from Delhi, Mumbai, Bangalore\n‚Ä¢ Taxi/bus available from airport\n\n**üöÇ By Train:**\n‚Ä¢ **Nangal Dam Railway Station** - Direct connectivity\n‚Ä¢ Trains from Delhi (6-7 hours), Mumbai (24 hours)\n‚Ä¢ **Anandpur Sahib** (20 km) - Alternative station\n\n**üöå By Road:**\n‚Ä¢ **From Delhi:** 280 km via NH-205 (5-6 hours)\n‚Ä¢ **From Chandigarh:** 60 km (1.5 hours)\n‚Ä¢ **From Amritsar:** 150 km (3 hours)\n‚Ä¢ Regular bus services available\n\n**üöï Local Transport:**\n‚Ä¢ Auto-rickshaws - ‚Çπ20-100 for city rides\n‚Ä¢ Cycle rickshaws - Eco-friendly option\n‚Ä¢ Taxi services - ‚Çπ15-20 per km\n‚Ä¢ Bike rentals - ‚Çπ300-500 per day\n\n**üõ£Ô∏è Road Conditions:** Well-maintained highways\n**‚õΩ Fuel:** Plenty of petrol pumps available"
              },
              activities: {
                keywords: ['activity', 'things to do', 'fun', 'adventure', 'recreation', 'sports'],
                response: "üéØ **Activities & Things to Do:**\n\n**üö∂ Nature Activities:**\n‚Ä¢ Hiking in Shivalik Hills\n‚Ä¢ Bird watching at Nangal Wetland\n‚Ä¢ Boating on Govind Sagar Lake\n‚Ä¢ Nature photography walks\n‚Ä¢ Sunrise/sunset viewing\n\n**üèõÔ∏è Cultural Experiences:**\n‚Ä¢ Visit local temples and gurudwaras\n‚Ä¢ Explore traditional markets\n‚Ä¢ Village cultural tours\n‚Ä¢ Local craft workshops\n‚Ä¢ Festival participation (seasonal)\n\n**üé£ Water Activities:**\n‚Ä¢ Fishing in the lake (with permits)\n‚Ä¢ Lakeside picnics\n‚Ä¢ Water sports (seasonal)\n‚Ä¢ Dam engineering tours\n\n**üë®‚Äçüë©‚Äçüëß‚Äçüë¶ Family Fun:**\n‚Ä¢ Park visits and playground time\n‚Ä¢ Local food tours\n‚Ä¢ Heritage walks\n‚Ä¢ Shopping for local handicrafts\n\n**What type of activities interest you most?**"
